body_html: @Nithanaroy you should create the issue through https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues => "New Issue" => "Bug/Performance Issue" and provide all required information there. In particular, as much as possible you should provide a minimal reproducible example. Your issue is currently missing information about system environment, TensorFlow version, and your example is not reproducible.
